<div class="OutlineElement Ltr  BCX0 SCXW201987949">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201987949 BCX0"><span class="TextRun SCXW201987949 BCX0" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="auto">This course emphasizes communicative evaluation and analysis. The overall goal of the course is to improve student ability to understand and produce extended discourse in English, especially in reading and writing contexts. Academic English vocabulary, recognizing and summarizing key points, critical thinking skills, and logical argumentation based on examples and evidence will be emphasized.</span><span class="EOP SCXW201987949 BCX0" data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}"> </span></p>
